  <RI_BookAbility_Slash.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>{PARENT_label}(을)를 읽은 후, 수련자 {STUDIER_labelShort}(이)가 삼단참을 배웠습니다!</RI_BookAbility_Slash.comps.CompBookStudiable.completedLetterText>
